OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A British man accused of public        
OL,6, disorder after joking about blowing up 
OL,7, a flight has gone on trial in Spain.   
OL,9,FAditya Verma made the comment on       
OL,10,FSnapchat on his way to the island of   
OL,11,FMenorca with friends in July 2022.     
OL,13,FThe message, sent before Mr Verma      
OL,14,Fdeparted Gatwick airport, read: "On my 
OL,15,Fway to blow up the plane (I'm a member 
OL,16,Fof the Taliban)."                      
OL,18,FMr Verma told a Madrid court on Monday:
OL,19,F"The intention was never to cause      
OL,20,Fpublic distress or cause public harm." 
